features: Fans will find western-style fun with this 12-inch tall Jessie figure with lasso accessory, inspired by Disney and Pixar's Toy Story movies.
It's a ropin' round-up with this button-activated oversized lasso. Not only can the Jessie figure shoot the two-part lasso, but aspiring cowboys and cowgirls can use it for roleplay.
Jessie is ready for any rodeo spotlight, with 13 movable joints providing deluxe posability. She wears her iconic cow-print chaps and her signature red hat is removable.
A lasso-worthy rattlesnake target stand is included. More cut-out cardboard targets are available on the box.
Makes a great gift for Toy Story fans 4 years and older.
body.description: This 12-inch Jessie, from Disney and Pixar's Toy Story, can rope in some oversized fun. She comes with 13 posable joints and a 2-piece lasso accessory! The red-haired heroine appears in her signature cow-print chaps and has a removable hat. The shooting lasso fits in her hand for button-activated fun and is slightly oversized, so it can also be used for roleplay! The pack includes a rattlesnake target stand to shoot at, and there are additional cut-out targets on the box. Makes a great gift for Toy Story fans 4 years and older. Colors and decorations may vary.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Ranging from 7-inch scale to 12-inch scale, action figures capture the charm of the Disney and Pixar movie characters they represent, with content-accurate design, deluxe detail and posability. With 3 Pixar characters from the same movie, Storyteller Packs are ready to relive cinematic moments or weave new creative tales. At 4-inch scale, they each have movie-accurate design. These character plush toys are instantly recognizable. In many sizes, from soft plushes to Cuutopia round plushes, they’re irresistibly huggable and ready for playtime or bedtime.
Adventures with Disney and Pixar With action figures, storyteller packs and plushes from Mattel, kids of all ages can recreate their favorite movie adventures. Discover a wide world of imagination!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Enough for a Collector
reviews.reviewText: I was surprised by this 12" Jessie with Lasso figure. I assumed that it was just a toy for kids, but in reality, this is a collector-quality Jesse Action Figure. I am impressed with both it quality and the packaging.Notes-- Jesse's lasso shoots out in order to try and lasso the snake! It is a fun addition to just having an action figure- Jesse is 12" tall and has fully poseable (with a removable cowgirl hat!)- The packaging is very nice - definitely not just standard packaging. The box opens up and a nice retro look to it.- High quality Jesse - one of my complaints about contemporary kid's toys is that they are made so cheaply. That is not the case with the Jesse by Mattel. The joints are fluid and move easily. There are no flaws in the coloring. It really does feel high quality... again.. like something a collector would want!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Daughter really liked it
reviews.reviewText: My daughter is a huge Toy Story fan but she didn't have any of the figures so when I saw this I figured I'd pick it up for her. It came packaged just fine with no defects that I could see. Getting it out it was a figure of Jessie, a rope with a launcher, a snake for target practice, and some other cutouts that can be used for shooting. She likes playing with Jessie but when we showed her how the rope shoots out that was her big thing. For a toy for a toddler, it is surprisingly good, lord knows how many times we had to lad it for her before she figured out how to use it. She had a blast with it and last night it got the honor of sleeping with her in bed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My Daughter Loves This Jessie!
reviews.reviewText: My daughter loved this Jessie doll from the moment she unwrapped it. It has an easy to open clamshell style box. I really like the packaging for this toy. There is no plastic involved in the packaging. It's all either cardboard or paper. Even the restraints used to keep Jessie in the box are made of paper. The toy itself is a lot of fun. It has multiple pieces of articulation and seems very durable. It's survived a couple of weeks of rough play from a 7 year old so far with no problem. The lasso shooter is easy to load and shoots surprisingly far. My daughter also likes that Jessie's hat is removable, and fits on the toy's head quite easily. Her only complaint is that the pull string ring on Jessie's back is molded to the toy. She would have liked if that were pullable here as well. Overall though, she loves it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality; Lots of movable joints; Big (12")
reviews.reviewText: Our toddler likes it! It's Jessie the Yodeling Cowgirl, standing at around 12 inches. There comes a cool removable red hat. The lasso shoots out of her hand when you press the top button. Even though it's not specifically designed for toddlers (package says 4+), our 27-month-old really likes it!Pros:1. The plastic is smooth and looks sturdy.2. Lots of movable joints – arms, shoulders, knees, legs, head, waist, and wrists.3. Well packaged and is giftable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 12" Jessie is large compared to a Barbie
reviews.reviewText: This figure of Toy Story's Jessie is 12" tall but it is not a normal Barbie size. Her whole body is large. She has movable arms and legs at the knees and elbows. She has a lasso action feature that shoots out of the rope after connecting it to her hand and then pushing button. A rattlesnake target stand is included. She's wearing her iconic outfit with her famous hat. Her outfit is part of her body, but hat is separate and removable. Even the box it comes in is very giftable. The front opens out to reveal Jessie and her accessories behind plastic.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great toy figure with action lasso
reviews.reviewText: This is larger than I was expecting. The doll measures 12" tall, but is a larger form than a Barbie doll. The lasso on this has roping action. If you like Toy Story or are a Toy Story collector, this is a must buy.
